Name: Rappler
Content:
One breezy February afternoon in San Jose Del Monte City, the Marcos slate Alyansa campaigned in the vote-rich province, and Camille Villar, heiress to the business and political empire, promised all the basic needs — housing, jobs, etc. — except for one: water. #PHVote

Name: Kiko Pangilinan
Content:
Maraming salamat, mga kabataang San Joseño! Ayon sa independent online survey ng Angat Kabataang San Joseño, tayo ang nanguna sa senatorial preferences ng kabataan sa San Jose del Monte, Bulacan para sa #Halalan2025!

Mahalaga ang boses ng kabataan sa darating na halalan!

Content:
